body.description: The Tommee Tippee First Bottle Solution baby bottle set is a simple essential bottle feeding set containing all the baby bottles and nipples you need from day one of your baby’s bottle feeding journey.With our award-winning** Closer to Nature baby bottle, switching between breast and bottle feeding has never been simpler. With our breast-like nipple and built-in anti-colic valve, it could just be the best thing for baby, since you! Inspired by mom, designed by experts.Loved by moms and babies, our easy latch-on, breast-like nipple feels closer to skin and mimics the natural flex and movement of a mom's breast for a comfortable feed. 95% of moms reported that their baby accepted the soft silicone nipple with skin-like feel and would recommend to others. *All Closer to Nature bottle nipples feature an anti-colic valve to prevent the symptoms of colic by ensuring your little one ingests more milk and less air. Together with the bottle’s sensitive valve, the wide bottle neck encourages your baby’s intuitive feeding action. Designed to be held in the most natural position during feeding, the compact shape of the bottle also allows baby to be closer to you.The wide neck bottle makes cleaning easy, and the bottles are suitable for use in the dishwasher, microwave and steam sterilisers. 100% BPA-free for complete peace of mind. The included travel lids and discs prevent spills or leaks when on the go.*Based on 2021 study of 524 parents who use Tommee Tippee bottles** Made for moms March 2020Which flow rate do I need?We offer different flow rates to keep up with your growing baby. Every baby is different but as a guide we suggest slow flow for 0+months, medium flow for 3+ months and fast flow for 6+ months. Closer to Nature nipples are only compatible with Closer to Nature bottles.How often should I replace the bottle nipples?We recommend changing your bottle nipples every two months and you should change them immediately if they're damaged or weak.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Anti-colic valve. The anti-colic valve in the nipple helps to reduce symptoms of colic by preventing excessive air from getting into your baby’s milk. Natural latch. Our bottle nipples are made from soft silicone and have a special breast-like shape that encourages a natural latch and prevents nipple confusion when switching between bottle and breast. Natural pace. The soft silicone nipple flexes and stretches like mom and allows your baby to feed comfortably at their own pace.

Most recommended baby bottle. Our Closer to Nature Anti-Colic bottles are #1 for easily switching between bottle and breast*. 100% leakproof. When the screw ring, nipple and cap are all secured, your baby bottle is completely mess-free and leakproof, even if it’s turned upside down or shaken. Easy clean and BPA free. These bottles are suitable for use in the dishwasher, microwave and sterilizers. All Tommee Tippee bottles are BPA- and phthalate-free for your ultimate reassurance.

Go with the flow. We offer different flow rates to keep up with your growing baby. Every baby is different but as a guide we suggest slow flow and vari flow for 0+months, medium flow for 3+ months and fast flow for 6+ months. Change me. Our nipples are silky soft. Change them if they get damaged or bitten by tiny teeth. Closer to Nature baby bottles are ONLY compatible with Closer to Nature nipples and cannot be used with Advanced Anti-Colic bottle nipples. Squeeze me. When assembling your baby bottle, hold the nipple up to the light to check the slit in the silicone isn’t sealed closed. If it has, pinch it gently between your fingers or with nipple tongs to re-open. If the valve has sealed closed, your bottle won’t vent properly.

This is a great bottle starter set. I was looking for new bottles because my one month old daughter was having trouble drinking from a bottle without it being a complete mess. She had the most success with the nipples that are designed for the Enfamil nursettes. I picked this set up to try because I like that it had different sizes as she moved to different formula amounts, as well as having other extras.There are four nipples in this set - two slow flow and two medium flow. The bottles are easy to hold and easy to clean because of the wide mouth. I have no problems reaching all the sides and bottom. The soother included is a great light weight small one for little babies. I also like that it includes the handle adapter for when she can hold things better.At first she was still messy when drinking from these bottles, but now at almost 3 months old she is managing the medium flow nipples well. I like that these should see us through her bottle needs.
Bouteille parfait pour un nouveau née
